      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty strong take lol. you're saying it's basically always bad? what about the idea that people need a sense of belonging to a common culture or country to actually follow laws and work together? isn't some level of national identity needed to prevent a country from just falling apart into chaos?",
